<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TolE0109">
<l>avaitām</l>
<l>meypiṟi tātaṉ mikutal kuṉṟaleṉ</l>
<l>ṟivveṉa moḻipa tiriyu māṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Among those,</l>
<l>as the initial sound of the coming word unites</l>
<l>with the final sound of the standing word,</l>
<l>[and] as a noun joins a noun,<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">peyar.</foreign></note></l>
<l>[or] a noun joins a verb<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">toḻil.</foreign></note></l>
<l>[or] a verb joins a noun</l>
<l>[or] a verb joins a verb,</l>
<l>there are four methods of word-sandhi<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">moḻipuṇar.</foreign></note></l>
<l>in three [of which] change takes place<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">tiripu.</foreign></note></l>
<l>and in one [of which] there is a no-change.<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">iyalpu.</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
